title: Malaysia maternal mortality ratio 2011 to 2018
yAxis: Maternal mortality ratio per hundred thousand live births
summary: This statistic presents the volume of money market instruments outstanding in the united from 2011 to 2018 . In 2018 , the volume of the money market instruments outstanding in the united was approximately 0.99 trillion u.s. dollars . The money market is an informal network of banks , brokers , dealers and financial institutions which are linked electronically .
gold: The statistic represents the maternal mortality ratio in Malaysia from 2011 to 2018 . In 2018 , the maternal mortality ratio in Malaysia was approximately 23.5 maternal deaths per one hundred thousand live births .
